text: The Sydney Swans are a professional Australian rules football club from Sydney, New South Wales, that plays in the Australian Football League (AFL). ==Club song== Cheer, cheer the red and the white, Honour the name by day and by night, Lift that noble banner high, Shake down the thunder from the sky Whether the odds be great or small, Swans will go in and win overall While her loyal sons are marching Onwards to victory. ==Related pages== * Australian rules football in New South Wales ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Australian rules football clubs in Australia
title: Sydney Swans
